{
  "texts": [
    "Taken together, Figure 4.",
    "(a) suggests that the null earnings effects are not simply the result of weak treatments-at either the firm or worker level.",
    "Workers in firms that adopt a more active, multifaceted approach to AI chatbots do not see differential earnings impacts.",
    "Nor do those who use the tools more frequently, adopted them earlier, or report large work-related benefits.",
    "Occupational Heterogeneity."
  ]
}